Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是联合国军队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取Throne的机师是阿里·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要瞧不起人到什么地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是个佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是补给先完成  还是联合国军队先来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样  都会导致在拉格朗治1发生战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备用零件也都备齐了  想的真周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获这台Gundam的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是顶武特务部队的谢尔盖·斯密尔诺夫中校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到「俄罗斯的暴熊」会亲自来接见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是法国第四独立外籍士兵机兵联队的加里·比亚吉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将参加Gundam扫荡作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想知道  你是如何捕获Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是商业机密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离抵达可视范围战斗宇宙域还有2000
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员  第一级战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部队  准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时刻终于到了  霍华德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到答案了吗  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我…我们受到了伊奥里亚·修亨贝格的嘱托
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就要以自己的意志为根除纷争而战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  我从来都没想过可以根除纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我们这有点夸张的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是好是坏  都深深地刻在了人们的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being  我们…有存在的意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊  就只有通过亲身经历才会真正理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密吗  发现联合国军队的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近的敌方运输舰确定为联合的弗吉尼亚级  3艘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离可视范围战斗域还有4200
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密一边利用资源卫星一边后退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  Virtue  准备防御战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames在托勒密上待命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不用这样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然上了锁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不是有点蛮干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是那种会听解释的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在上次战斗中被他救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  这次由我来保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios在线性加速带固定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  阿雷路亚·哈普提兹姆  开始迎击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS从敌方运输舰出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  提耶利亚·厄德  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌MS  拟GN Drive搭载型  26台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌方MS部队中发现Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全体机师传达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击的Gundam只有2台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采用245阵型应对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包围后将他们全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  就等我的战果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成功  一定要成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  各位都很有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始先制攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新装备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于尾部推进器  机动性提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机  不要打乱阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用E计划  采取各个击破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Throne吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后随你们便了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是索玛·佩丽丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  尾部推进器受损
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在与可能是超兵的MS交战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue受到了敌方MS的集中攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Gundam后退
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥  能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN Armor进行对舰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说按照你的战术办事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗  不好意思  陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·萨谢斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠落吧  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…头疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波被我切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他们  阿雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T…TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上…上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子剩余量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你干的好事  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敌机迅速靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对援兵进行集中炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  现在可没法进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来压制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始炮击  开始炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此转为对舰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂  以你那样的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的关心表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  TRANS-AM的时限…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嫩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  Virtue  结束TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重新补充粒子之前  机体性能下降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已突破敌方MS部队  进入了对舰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮他一把…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方MA靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用线性加农炮应战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气对敌中心进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norfolk  被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部队还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要180秒才能抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Throne…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·萨谢斯吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为右眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是KPSA的萨谢斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  克鲁吉斯的小鬼告诉你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爱尔兰指使自杀式炸弹恐怖袭击的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中东会反对AEU的轨道电梯建设  这不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然连累了无辜的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑起根除纷争的恐怖份子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会接受处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要在击败你之后！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  地点确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除对接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用TRANS-AM前往战斗宇宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能原谅
